  "texts": [
    "Sets C, D, and E comprised information from five patients.",
    "The EEG traces for set D were gathered in the epileptogenic zone.",
    "Set C was recorded in the other hemisphere of the brain, where the hippocampus is formed.",
    "Unlike Sets C and D, which contain EEG signals recorded during seizure-free periods (interictal) (ictal), Set E's EEG data were exclusively recorded during seizure activity.",
    "For both datasets, around 80% of data has been taken for training models and 20% of data is considered for testing the models."
